author: @kaah6162
content: Your comment has proved your illiteracy on indigenous tribes in Brazil. Many indigenous reserves are kept by the federal government especially in the region where you live. My family is mixed race with white German and indigenous in Brazil.  Just like in USA and Canada, the tribes are under secret maintance by the Federal power but the media headline only the Amazon rainforest as the only part of Brazil keeping tribes as reserve.
